    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lexicon</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compi is a visual constructed language with an extensive Lexicon. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine the symbols in 2D space to build sentences. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278200/extras/3fcbb0a7570e4b9d0a60007051dbfab4.avif?t=1730761349\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278200/extras_big/3fcbb0a7570e4b9d0a60007051dbfab4.avif?t=1730761349 width=800 height=288 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ontology</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For this game an ontology was used, with a hierarchy of concepts (for example object-&gt;person-&gt;human), and a database of instances of those objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278200/extras/1643fd09944fc8d9634a44aa187baeb8.avif?t=1730761349\" width=404 height=134 /></span></p>",
